text.autoconfig.sbutils.title: sbutils Options
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.messagePr: The prefix that appears before sbutils messages. The '@' will be replaced with 'sbutils'.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.sbutilsCo: The color of the sbutils name in messages.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.prefixCol: The color of the characters surrounding 'sbutils' in the message prefix.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.valueColo: The color of values in sbutils messages.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.autoAdver: Automatically sends messages from a file.
The txt file containing your /skyblock advertisements.
The txt file containing your /economy advertisements.
The txt file containing your /classic advertisements.
The delay between joining and sending an advert. (Seconds)
Only sends adverts from the account(s) specified in the whitelist.
A list of accounts that may send adverts if 'Use Advert Whitelist' is enabled.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.joinComma: Automatically sends commands when you join the server.
The delay between joining the server and sending the commands.
Detects mentions of words/phrases in chat.
Notifies you with a sound when something is mentioned in chat.
The sound played when something is mentioned in chat.
Whether to change the color of mentions in chat.
The color to highlight mentions with.
Doesn't notify you about server messages.
Doesn't notify you about your own messages.
Ignores the sender (the prefix/name of the player) when checking for mentions.
Notifies you when your username is mentioned in chat.
A list of strings you would like to be notified for.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.noGmt.noG: Replaces GMT date/time in /mail and /email with a preferred timezone.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.noGmt.tim: Set a preferred time zone, or leave blank to use system time.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.noGmt.sho: Displays the new time zone in parenthesis next to the date/time.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.enchantAl: Whether to use the built in /enchantall command, or send enchants individually.
The delay between sending enchant commands. (Seconds)
The number of commands to be executed before a cooldown is initiated. (To avoid spam kick)
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.chatAppen: Adds the specified prefix to all the messages you send.
The prefix to add to your messages.
Adds the specified suffix to all the messages you send.
The suffix to add to your messages.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.chatFilte: Whether tip messages should be filtered from chat.
Whether advancement messages should be filtered from chat.
Whether player welcome messages should be filtered from chat.
Whether friend join messages should be filtered from chat.
Whether island MOTD messages should be filtered from chat.
Whether player vote messages should be filtered from chat.
Whether player vote reward messages should be filtered from chat.
Whether raffle messages should be filtered from chat.
Whether crate opening messages should be filtered from chat.
Whether 'perished in void' messages should be filtered from chat.
Whether SkyChat messages should be filtered from chat.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.chatLogge: Whether to log transaction messages from your shops.
Whether to log transaction messages from other players' shops.
Whether to log incoming private messages.
Whether to log outgoing private messages.
Whether to log players visiting your island.
Whether to log messages from drop party events.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.eventNoti: Shows a title when a vote party llama appears at spawn.
Plays a sound when a vote party llama appears at spawn.
The sound played when a vote party llama appears at spawn.
Shows a title when a wandering trader appears at spawn.
Plays a sound when a wandering trader appears at spawn.
The sound played when a wandering trader appears at spawn.
Automatically switches to a new pickaxe when the current durability gets too low.
The durability to switch to a new pickaxe at.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.autoFix.a: Automatically fixes the most damaged items in your inventory over time.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.autoFix.m: The maximum durability percentage an item can have and be fixed.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.autoFix.f: How long to wait for a response before sending the fix command again.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.autoFix.m: The maximum amount of times to retry the fix command if the server isn't responding.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.toolSaver: Prevents usage of tools after a certain durability.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.antiPlace: Prevents the placement of heads that have custom names.
Prevents the placement of grass blocks.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.autoComma: Repeatedly executes a command with a set delay.
The minimum delay between commands if there are multiple in the list.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.autoReply: The response to send to private messages.
The delay between responses if multiple people message you at once. (Seconds)
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.autoRaffl: Automatically buys raffle tickets when you log in and when the raffle ends.
The amount of raffle tickets to purchase on /skyblock. (Max. 2)
The amount of raffle tickets to purchase on /economy. (Max. 5)
If you don't have enough grass in your inventory, how often it should check for more. (Seconds)
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.autoPriva: Up to two names to put on private signs. Yours is included automatically.
Automatically enchants books and diamond pickaxes with Silk Touch.
The tool that Auto Silk will target.
The delay between each enchanting action.
Adds a button to the enchantment screen for toggling Auto Silk.
The position of the Auto Silk button.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.autoCrate: The type of crate to target.
After the current crate finishes, how long to wait before opening the next.
The maximum distance from the crate.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.autoKit.a: If multiple kits are to be claimed at the same time, the delay between each command.
The amount of additional delay after the predicted kit reset time, to account for inaccuracies. Only applies to non 24-hour kits.
Delay used to account for system time desync when claiming 24-hour kits. Changing this is not recommended.
text.autoconfig.sbutils.option.staffDete: Whether you should receive notifications when staff members join.
Whether you should receive notifications when staff members leave.
Whether to play sounds when staff members join/leave.
The sound played when staff join/leave.
